highlights.text: Terence Lam has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “夏日之子” is the highest at #20.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1548 days straight.
“淘汰” by Eason Chan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 42 spots at #130.
